          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The yield was monitored by two out-of-",
                "plane detectors, one above and one below the beam. The",
                "total number of counts in these detectors was used to",
                "normalize the observed intensities. the cross sections",
                "were determined in relative units. By comparing our",
                " (p,d) results with absolute cross section measurements",
                "at 30 MeV( see Rel-Ref) and relating them through a",
                "detailed study to each other, was obtained an absolute",
                "normalization with an estimated accuracy +-25%,",
                " 100 relative units correspond to 610 mu-b/sr."
              ]
            }
          ],
